# 📊 Sales Data Analysis Dashboard

This repository contains a Power BI dashboard and supporting Excel dataset used to analyze and visualize business sales performance.

## 📝 Project Description

This project showcases a dynamic sales analytics dashboard created in **Power BI** using real-world sales data. It provides insights into sales trends, product performance, regional analysis, and customer segmentation.

## 📁 Files Included

- `Sales Data Live.pbix` – Power BI dashboard file
- `Sales data Live.xlsx` – Excel dataset used in the dashboard

## 📈 Dashboard Features

- 🚀 Total Sales, Profit, and Quantity Overview  
- 🛍️ Top-Selling Products by Revenue and Units  
- 🌍 Regional Sales Breakdown  
- 📅 Monthly and Yearly Sales Trends  
- 👥 Customer Segmentation and Performance

## 🛠 Tools & Technologies

- **Power BI Desktop** – For data visualization and report creation  
- **Microsoft Excel** – For storing and managing the sales data

